675
00:43:32,550 --> 00:43:34,310
Chviličku.

676
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:40,220
Nemáš tisícovku?

677
00:43:40,220 --> 00:43:41,270
Ne.

678
00:43:41,270 --> 00:43:43,130
Ani pětistovku?

679
00:43:43,820 --> 00:43:45,250
Ne.

680
00:43:45,250 --> 00:43:47,540
